name: A Crack In Mind
description:
This place in particular has helped me grow stronger mentally. On my random solitude hikes, I would often go to this place to see the vastness of the Ozarks span out across the landscape. 
Between these cliff facings, you would often find big cracks which were large enough to walk into.
There was my curiosity pulling me forward dissolving the crack between the left side and right side of my brain as I was "just there". And there was "this" experiencing the experience.
